name: Durango Web Pro
description: Durango Web Pro offers web design
overview:
Durango Web Pro offers web design, web hosting, and search engine optimization for web sites. Principal, Terry McClain, is Located in Durango, Colorado, offering web design for clients nationwide.

Durango Web Pro was founded by Terry McClain. He brings to the Design and Development process over 22 years of experience working with small businesses and Information Technology. Seventeen of these years were spent as the founder and President of a company that grew under his leadership to become one of the largest Computer Sales and Service companies supporting small business networks in the South Puget Sound.

Having worked with hundreds of small businesses over these years has helped him develop an expertise in how to utilize Information Technology to grow a business. After successfully growing and selling his previous company, he has been focused for the last 5 years in programming with an emphasis on web development solutions. He has a gift and passion for web site design that he shares through his work.
